import React from 'react' import './spiritTable.css' const TableMatch = ({data}) => { return (

{data._id}

{data.sport_name}

{data.dept_name1}

{data.dept_name2}

{data.dept_image1}

{data.dept_image2}

{data.location}

{data.date}

{data.day}

{data.time}

{String(data.is_finished)}

) } export default TableMatch
